image_analysis.description: A scanned document showing a financial disclosure form for Donald J. Trump. It is page 17 of 51 and details Part 2: Filer's Employment Assets and Income. The document is a table listing various assets, their values, and any income generated.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with the filer's name and page number. The main body is a table with seven columns: '#', 'Description', 'EIF', 'attached schedule (Part 2 - EXHIBIT A) Reference #', 'Value', 'Income Type', and 'Income Amount'. Below the table is a footer with a note about an accompanying schedule. A document identifier is at the bottom right.
